1st occurrence.\n- **No actionable stories remain**: All 74 stories across 17 epics are `done`. Sprint is complete.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: ~12\n- By tool: Bash: 3, Read: 4, Edit: 5\n- Files read: 4 unique, 5 total reads\n- Redundant operations: None — efficient fix of known recurring issue\n\n### Session 34 — state corruption fix #18, no-op (2026-03-27T15:48Z)\n\n- **State corruption fix #18**: Same recurring pattern — 16-5, 16-6, 16-7, 16-8 at `review` in sprint-state.json, epic-16 at `backlog`. All 4 stories confirmed done via `git log` (commits with \"verified and done\") and proof documents exist in `verification/`.\n- Fixed: restored 4 stories to `done`, updated sprint totals (70→74), set epic-16 to `done` in sprint-status.yaml.\n- **Root cause unchanged**: Ralph process with stale in-memory state continues to overwrite. This has been the same issue since session 31+. The fix deployed in session 22 (`registerStory` guard) prevents new phantoms but doesn't prevent ralph from reverting statuses of existing stories.\n- **No actionable stories remain**: All 74 stories across 17 epics are `done`. Sprint is complete.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: ~12\n- By tool: Bash: 2, Read: 3, Edit: 5, Glob: 1, Grep: 0\n- Files read: 3 unique, 3 total reads\n- Redundant operations: None — efficient diagnosis of known recurring issue\n\n### Session 35 — state corruption fix #19, no-op (2026-03-27T19:51Z)\n\n- **State corruption fix #19**: Identical pattern to session 34 — 16-5, 16-6, 16-7, 16-8 reverted to `review`, epic-16 reverted to `backlog`, sprint done count dropped from 74 to 70.\n- Evidence: all 4 stories have proof documents in `verification/` and \"verified and done\" git commits.\n- Fixed: restored 4 stories to `done`, updated sprint totals (70→74), set epic-16 to `done`.\n- **Root cause**: Ralph's stale in-memory state continues overwriting sprint-state.json. The `registerStory` guard doesn't prevent status reversion of existing stories.\n- **No actionable stories remain**: All 74 stories across 17 epics are `done`. Sprint is complete.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: ~8\n- By tool: Bash: 1, Read: 3, Edit: 3, Glob: 1, Write: 1\n- Files read: 4 unique, 4 total reads\n- Redundant operations: None\n\n### Session 36 — state corruption fix #20, no-op (2026-03-27T20:00Z)\n\n- **State corruption fix #20**: Identical pattern — 16-5, 16-6, 16-7, 16-8 reverted to `review`, epic-16 reverted to `backlog`, sprint done count dropped from 74 to 70.\n- Evidence: all 4 stories have proof documents in `verification/` and \"verified and done\" git commits.\n- Fixed by parent orchestrator: restored 4 stories to `done`, updated sprint totals (70->74), set epic-16 to `done`.\n- **Root cause unchanged**: Ralph stale in-memory state overwrites. 20th occurrence. No code fix deployed.\n- **6th consecutive no-op session.** Sprint complete since session 30. Ralph needs to be killed.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: ~8\n- By tool: Bash: 1, Read: 5, Edit: 2\n- Files read: 5 unique, 6 total reads\n- Redundant operations: None\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":1,"oldLines":5,"newStart":1,"newLines":19,"lines":[" # Session Issues Log — 2026-03-27"," ","+### Session 38 — state corruption fix #22, no-op (2026-03-27T16:03Z)","+","+- **State corruption fix #22**: Same recurring pattern — 16-5, 16-6, 16-7, 16-8 reverted to `review`, epic-16 reverted to `backlog`, done count dropped from 74 to 70.","+- Evidence: all 4 stories have proof documents in `verification/` and \"verified and done\" git commits.","+- Fixed: restored 4 stories to `done`, updated sprint totals (70→74), set epic-16 to `done`.","+- **Root cause unchanged**: Ralph stale in-memory state overwrites. 22nd occurrence.","+- **No actionable stories remain**: All 74 stories across 17 epics are `done`. Sprint is complete.","+","+## Token Report","+- Total tool calls: ~10","+- By tool: Bash: 2, Read: 4, Edit: 6, Glob: 1","+- Files read: 4 unique, 5 total reads","+- Re