{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_017BSxGbF9X7mfoGyFT4CgYr","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Harness Cost Report\n     2→\n     3→Total API-equivalent cost: $690.16\n     4→Total API calls: 5086\n     5→Average cost per story: $3.49 (155 stories)\n     6→\n     7→## Cost by Token Type\n     8→\n     9→| Type | Tokens | Rate | Cost | % |\n    10→|------|--------|------|------|---|\n    11→| Cache reads | 281,039,441 | $1.50/MTok | $421.56 | 61% |\n    12→| Cache writes | 8,586,284 | $18.75/MTok | $160.99 | 23% |\n    13→| Output | 1,432,301 | $75/MTok | $107.42 | 16% |\n    14→| Input | 12,573 | $15/MTok | $0.19 | 0% |\n    15→\n    16→## Cost by Phase\n    17→\n    18→| Phase | Calls | Cost | % |\n    19→|-------|-------|------|---|\n    20→| verify | 2984 | $376.95 | 54.6% |\n    21→| orchestrator | 668 | $139.31 | 20.2% |\n    22→| retro | 498 | $70.77 | 10.3% |\n    23→| create-story | 344 | $36.58 | 5.3% |\n    24→| code-review | 321 | $36.49 | 5.3% |\n    25→| dev-story | 271 | $30.07 | 4.4% |\n    26→\n    27→## Cost by Tool\n    28→\n    29→| Tool | Calls | Cost | % |\n    30→|------|-------|------|---|\n    31→| Bash | 2075 | $255.16 | 37.0% |\n    32→| Read | 1004 | $135.18 | 19.6% |\n    33→| Edit | 688 | $89.19 | 12.9% |\n    34→| Agent | 455 | $60.27 | 8.7% |\n    35→| Skill | 142 | $50.98 | 7.4% |\n    36→| Grep | 340 | $39.86 | 5.8% |\n    37→| Write | 146 | $26.46 | 3.8% |\n    38→| TodoWrite | 111 | $15.24 | 2.2% |\n    39→| Glob | 93 | $14.32 | 2.1% |\n    40→| ToolSearch | 28 | $3.10 | 0.4% |\n    41→\n    42→## Top 10 Most Expensive Stories\n    43→\n    44→| Story | Calls | Cost | % |\n    45→|-------|-------|------|---|\n    46→| unknown | 733 | $149.34 | 21.6% |\n    47→| 14-5-stack-aware-verify-dockerfile | 190 | $23.63 | 3.4% |\n    48→| 14-4-observability-backend-choice | 192 | $22.13 | 3.2% |\n    49→| 1-1-foo | 172 | $21.35 | 3.1% |\n    50→| 8-9-semgrep-rules-rust-observability | 121 | $17.10